#DStv403  DURBAN - KwaZulu-Natal continues to count the cost of the floods that have swept across the province.  KZN Health MEC Nomagugu Simelane has confirmed the latest figures. #DStv403  According to KZN Health MEC Nomagugu Simelane, the death toll from the KZN floods has risen to 253. Meanwhile, residents who have lost their homes are in desperate need of help. National Treasury has agreed to give KZN money to recover from the disastrous floods, according to the province's Finance MEC, Nomusa Dube-Ncube. eNCA's reporters Dasen Thathiah and Siphamandla Goge are monitoring the latest developments. #eNCA Courtesy #DStv403